!terminal colors ------------------------------------------------------------

! tangoesque scheme
*background:  #323232
*foreground:  #FFFFFF
! Black
*color0:      #2E3436
*color8:      #555753
! Red
*color1:      #CC0000
*color9:      #EF2929
! Green
*color2:      #4E9A06
*color10:     #8AE234
! Yellow
*color3:      #C4A000
*color11:     #FCE94F
! Blue
*color4:      #3465A4
*color12:     #729FCF
! Mangenta
*color5:      #75507B
*color13:     #AD7FA8
! Cyan 
*color6:      #06989A
